'''Latika Garboren''' was a woman who lived in the [[Taung Heights]] in [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. She was a self-professed "history nut", having a great interest in history. In [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]], she noticed that a dollop of [[pastebread]] she was preparing resembled the [[Sith acolyte emblem|emblem]] of a [[Sith acolyte/Legends|Sith Acolyte]]. She first tried to contact the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]], but failing that, contacted [[Coruscant Security Force/Legends|local security]] instead. Constabulary detective [[Dherik Rule]] investigated it for her, and found that there was no case to pursue.

